title: 83: Four Superpowers I Learned from Stan Lee
description:
I wanted to make this special episode to tribute to our superhero friend, Stan Lee. I’m bringing this episode to you from New York City, where he co-created some of my very favorite superheroes of all time.


In this episode, I’m going to share with you FOUR superpowers, mental/mindset superpowers, that I learned from the legend himself.


** Do you want to stay up to date with every new episode and get my brand new Kwik Brain Accelerator Program? Go to www.KwikBrain.com/podcast to get instant access. **
